doctype html
html
	head
		title Dive Buddy Request
		link(
			rel='stylesheet'
			type='text/css'
			integrity='sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u'
			crossorigin='anonymous'
			href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css'
		)
	body
		div(class='container')
			h1 Dive Buddy Request

			p Hi #{friendFriendlyName},

			p
				| You have a new dive buddy request from&nbsp;
				strong #{userFriendlyName}
				| &nbsp;over at&nbsp;
				a(href=`${siteUrl}`) BottomTime
				| ! To accept this request you can click&nbsp;
				a(href=`${approveUrl}`) here
				| . Or, if you wish you can decline the request by clicking&nbsp;
				a(href=`${rejectUrl}`) here
				| .

			p
				| Alternatively, you can head on over to the site and manage your list of dive buddies
				| from the Friends page of your account.

			p Cheers,
			p The BottomTime Team

			p
				small
					em Copyright &copy; Chris Carleton, 2019
